body:
Just found a minimal test case that can always crash Electron on OS X!

Take `electron-quick-start` and add the following to the end of `main.js`:

``` js
setTimeout(function () {
  mainWindow.setAspectRatio(0)
  mainWindow.setFullScreen(true)
}, 3000)

setTimeout(function () {
  mainWindow.setFullScreen(false)
}, 6000)
```
